  ${
    $d N k $.  $d X k $.
    $( Lemma for ~ bpolydif .  Calculate a trivial case.  (Contributed by Scott
       Fenton, 16-May-2014.) $)
    bpolydiflem1 $p |- ( N = 1 -> ( ( ph /\ X e. CC /\ ps ) -> ( ( ( ( X + 1 )
        ^ N ) - ( X ^ N ) ) - sum_ k e. ( 0 ... ( N - 1 ) ) ( ( N _C k ) x. ( (
        ( k BernPoly ( X + 1 ) ) - ( k BernPoly X ) ) / ( ( N - k ) + 1 ) ) ) )
        = ( N x. ( X ^ ( N - 1 ) ) ) ) ) $=
      ( wcel c1 caddc co cexp cmin cc0 cbc cbernpoly cdiv cmul wceq c2 opreq12d
      syl6eq cc w3a cfz csu ax-1cn subid1i peano2cn exp1 syl pncan2 mpan2 eqtrd
      cv bernpoly0 opreq1d opreq2d subidi opreq1i 2cn 2ne0 div0i opreq2i mul01i
      eqtri exp0 mulid1i 3eqtr4a 3ad2ant2 opreq2 opreq1 adantr sumeq12dv cvv cz
      oprex 0z df-2 syl6eqr cn0 1nn0 bcn0 ax-mp fsum1i mp2an id eqeq12d syl5ibr
